programme.title: Joshua O Joshua

programme.title: Sooryavanshi
programme.desc: With the looming threat of a terrorist attack on Mumbai, ATS chief Sooryavanshi embarks on a mission to hunt for 600 kgs of missing RDX and the conspiring perpetrators.

programme.title: Sooryavanshi
programme.desc: Saat sekelompok teroris mengancam akan menyerang Mumbai, kepala ATS Sooryavanshi memulai misi untuk memburu 600 kg RDX yang hilang dan para pelaku yang bersekongkol.

programme.title: Radha Mohan
programme.desc: Radha, a cheerful girl, is head over heels for Mohan, a cynical businessman, despite being aware of the fact that he has a daughter. However, she believes that she can turn him into a good man.

programme.title: Bhagya Lakshmi
programme.desc: Berasal dari keluarga Hindu Punjabi kelas menengah, Bajwa siap untuk menikahkan putri mereka Lakshmi dengan Varun. Namun, saat mencapai mandap dengan bus, orang tua Lakshmi, Kuljeet dan Manoj, meninggal dalam kecelakaan, membuat Lakshmi putus asa dan patah hati. Di sisi lain, bibi Lakshmi, Rano ingin merebut properti Manoj. Dia meminta asisten Manoj, Guru Charan untuk membuka brankas untuk mendapatkan uang, namun, dia menolaknya dan mengatakan bahwa keinginan terakhir Manoj adalah agar Lakshmi menikah dan setelah Rano menyelesaikan keinginan terakhirnya, dia dapat mengambil semuanya. programme.title: Executioners From Shaolin
programme.desc: The White-Browed Priest supports the brutal Qing government, burning down Shaolin Temple and hunting its disciples. Hung from Shaolin falls in love with Fang while escaping from the hunt and he is killed by the Priest.

programme.title: Executioners From Shaolin
programme.desc: Pendeta Alis Putih mendukung pemerintah Qing yang kejam, dan membakar kuil Shaolin serta memburu para muridnya. Hung dari Shaolin jatuh cinta pada Fang saat melarikan diri dan ia dibunuh oleh sang Pendeta.

programme.title: The Kid With The Golden Arm
programme.desc: The government hires Yang to escort a cargo of gold to a famine stricken area. The Chi Sha gang, with one of their best fighters, Golden Arm, announce their intention to hijack it by killing one of Yang's employees.

programme.title: The Kid With The Golden Arm
programme.desc: Pemerintah mempekerjakan Yang untuk mengawal muatan emas ke daerah yang dilanda kelaparan. Geng Chi Sha, dengan salah satu petarung terbaik mereka, Golden Arm, berniat melakukan pembajakan dan membunuh karyawan Yang.

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Set on the eve of the Japanese invasion of HK, this tragic Shaw Brothers romance stars Li Ting and Kwan Shan as young lovers torn apart by war.

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Berlatar pada malam penyerbuan Jepang di Hong Kong, film tentang kisah cinta yang tragis produksi Shaw Brothers ini dibintangi oleh Li Ting dan Kwan Shan sebagai sepasang kekasih yang terpisahkan oleh perang.

programme.title: Brave Archer And His Mate
programme.desc: Guo Jing and Huang Rong raise the son of his sworn brother Yang Kang and named him Yang Guo. To prevent Yang Guo from taking revenge for his father's death, Huang Rong bans him from learning martial arts.

programme.title: Brave Archer And His Mate
programme.desc: Guo Jing dan Huang Rong mengasuh putra saudara angkatnya Yang Kang dan memberinya nama Yang Gou. Demi mencegah Yan Gou membalas dendam atas kematian ayahnya, Huang Rong melarangnya mempelajari seni bela diri.

programme.title: Melody Of Love
programme.desc: This delightful romance story tells the story of three doctors pursuing three beauties who play hard-to-get in the 'a-go-go' era of the 70s.

programme.title: Melody Of Love
programme.desc: Kisah asmara yang mempesona ini bercerita tentang tiga dokter yang mengejar tiga gadis cantik di era musik 'a-go-go' pada tahun '70-an.

programme.title: The Twin Swords
programme.desc: Jimmy Wang Yu plays Kwei Wu who happens upon a kidnapping with his wife Kan Lien-chu at the Red Lotus Temple. Kan sends Kwei to go for reinforcements while she stays to fight the kidnappers.

programme.title: The Twin Swords
programme.desc: Jimmy Wang Yu berperan sebagai Kwei Wu menyaksikan sebuah penculikan bersama dengan istrinya Kan Lien-chu di Red Lotus Temple. Kan meminta Kwei pergi mencari bantuan saat ia berusaha melawan para penculik.

programme.title: Return Of The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Sequel to the John Lo Mar/Chang Yang original finds immigrant Yeh Feng leaving jail to live with crooked uncle Wang Sha, but his girlfriend Ai Ti has married an abusive husband.

programme.title: Return Of The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Film sekuel ini bercerita tentang imigran Yeh Feng yang kabur dari penjara untuk tinggal bersama paman Wang Sha yang jahat. Namun, ternyata kekasihnya, Ai Ti, telah menikah dengan seorang pria yang kasar.

programme.title: Masked Avengers
programme.desc: Masked killers are wreaking havoc and instilling terror with their vicious weapons of choice: razor-sharp, gut-shattering tridents. Only three fearless fighters dare investigate.

programme.title: Masked Avengers
programme.desc: Para pembunuh bertopeng membuat kekacauan dan menebar teror dengan bersenjatakan trisula tajam yang mampu mengoyak tubuh manusia. Hanya tiga pendekar pemberani yang bersedia mencari tahu identitas mereka.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: An award winning movie for best script and best editing. Another tale of a Sino-Japanese war that artistically and emotional triumphed, it clearly portrays the life of wartime.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: Film peraih penghargaan untuk naskah dan penyuntingan terbaik ini menceritakan kisah lain dari Perang Tiongkok-Jepang yang menggambarkan dengan jelas kehidupan masa perang secara artistik dan emosional.

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Based on the classic Ming Dynasty novel The Water Margin, Three Sinners is a Huangmei Opera about love, betrayal, murder, and redemption.

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Berdasarkan novel klasik era Dinasti Ming, The Water Margin, Three Sinner adalah sebuah Opera Huangmei tentang cinta, pengkhianatan, pembunuhan, dan penebusan dosa.

programme.title: Legendary Weapons Of China
programme.desc: Lei Kung, the leader of the Boxer Clan in Yunnan, dissolves the clan to save his disciples before going into self-exile.

programme.title: Legendary Weapons Of China
programme.desc: Lei Kung, pemimpin Klan Petinju di Yunnan, membubarkan sebuah klan untuk menyelamatkan murid-muridnya sebelum pergi mengasingkan diri.

programme.title: What Price Honesty?
programme.desc: He Zhong Heng, Luo Zhang and Ying Hao are assigned by the Imperial court as law enforcers. However, things take a turn when they discover corruption among officers.

programme.title: What Price Honesty?
programme.desc: He Zhong Heng, Luo Zhang, dan Ying Hao ditugaskan oleh pengadilan Kekaisaran sebagai penegak hukum. Namun, keadaan berubah ketika mereka menemukan korupsi di antara para petugas.

programme.title: Death Valley
programme.desc: A hired killer unknowingly makes friends with the man he's been sent to assassinate.

programme.title: Carry On Doctors And Nurses
programme.desc: Director Chan Friend created this delightful variation on the British 'Carry On!' film series. It can certainly make you laugh with all the comical acts happened in the Hospital!

programme.title: Carry On Doctors And Nurses
programme.desc: Director Chan Friend created this delightful variation on the British 'Carry On!' film series. It can certainly make you laugh with all the comical acts happened in the Hospital!

programme.title: Carry On Doctors And Nurses
programme.desc: Sutradara Chan Friend membuat variasi yang menarik dalam film seri asal Inggris 'Carry On!'. Film ini akan membuat Anda tertawa dengan semua aksi lucu yang terjadi di Rumah Sakit!

programme.title: Carry On Doctors And Nurses
programme.desc: Sutradara Chan Friend membuat variasi yang menarik dalam film seri asal Inggris 'Carry On!'. Film ini akan membuat Anda tertawa dengan semua aksi lucu yang terjadi di Rumah Sakit!

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: Ti Lung who lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with his brothers the Black Snake and the Yellow Snake, have been trying to turn into humans for a thousand years.

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: Ti Lung yang hidup di Gunung Ular Kwangsi bersama dengan saudaranya, Ular Hitam dan Ular Kuning, telah berusaha untuk berubah menjadi manusia selama seribu tahun.

programme.title: Enchanting Shadow
programme.desc: A young scholar spends the night in a creepy temple that is said to be haunted. He doesn't believe in the rumors, but after running into a Taoist swordsman, he meets a beautiful lady ghost.

programme.title: Enchanting Shadow
programme.desc: Seorang sarjana muda bermalam di sebuah kuil menyeramkan yang konon berhantu. Ia tidak percaya dengan rumor itu namun setelah menemui seorang pendekar pedang Taoisme, ia bertemu dengan sesosok hantu nan cantik.

programme.title: Summer Heat
programme.desc: The heavenly Jenny Hu plays the seductive Judy, who juggles three different men: a rich husband, a sexy playboy and sensitive intellectual, in her search for money, sex and love.

programme.title: Summer Heat
programme.desc: Si cantik Jenny Hu berperan sebagai Judy, sang penggoda yang merayu tiga pria berbeda: seorang pria kaya, seorang playboy seksi, dan seorang pria terpelajar nan sensitif dalam pencariannya akan uang, seks dan cinta.

programme.title: Killer Darts
programme.desc: Rampaging bandits are raping and pillaging all over peaceful Chinese villages until the grieving dart master Liu Wen Lung sets out with his student, son, and servant to avenge his murdered wife and set things right.

programme.title: Killer Darts
programme.desc: Sekawanan bandit brutal memperkosa dan menjarah di desa-desa Tiongkok. Liu Wen, ahli panah yang tengah berduka, beraksi bersama murid, anak, dan pelayannya guna membalas kematian istrinya dan mengembalikan kedamaian.

programme.title: Crocodile River
programme.desc: This story has a Romeo and Juliet flavour. Two families who hate each other live across the opposite sides of a river filled with crocodiles and do not bother to have a bridge built.

programme.title: The Deadly Breaking Sword
programme.desc: Warrior Tuan Chang Qing meets courtesan Liu Yin Xi in a small town. Liu pleads Tuan to kill the underworld master Guo Tian Sheng, known as the 'Killer Doctor', in order to avenge the death of her fiance.

programme.title: The Deadly Breaking Sword
programme.desc: Prajurit Tuan Chang Qing bertemu wanita penghibur Liu Yin Xi di sebuah kota kecil. Liu meminta Tuan untuk membunuh Guo Tian Sheng, yang dikenal sebagai 'Dokter Pembunuh', untuk membalas kematian tunangannya.

programme.title: The Scandalous Warlord
programme.desc: General Feng occupies the city of Shandong, and soldiers and civilians alike welcome him without knowing his tyrannical and lustful nature.

programme.title: The Scandalous Warlord
programme.desc: Jenderal Feng menguasai kota Shandong. Tentara dan warga sipil di sana menyambutnya tanpa mengetahui sifat kejam dan nafsunya yang menyeramkan.

programme.title: The Flying Dagger
programme.desc: The Yu family and the Green Dragon clan became enemies when the Yu daughter killed the clan head's son, who was a rapist and murderer. The Green Dragon leader wounds the head of the Yu family with his flying daggers.

programme.title: The Flying Dagger
programme.desc: Keluarga Yu dan klan Naga Hijau bermusuhan saat putri dari keluarga Yu membunuh putra kepala klan yang merupakan pemerkosa dan pembunuh. Pemimpin klan Naga Hijau melukai kepala keluarga Yu dengan belati terbangnya.

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: Back in 1973 the stock market was skyrocketing, but HK's social issues continued to worsen. TVB and Shaw Bros' biggest stars come together for this ingenious tongue-in-cheek tale.

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: Di tahun 1973, bursa saham meroket, namun masalah-masalah sosial di Hong Kong terus memburuk. Bintang-bintang besar TVB dan Shaw Brothers bersatu dalam kisah yang lucu ini.

programme.title: The Five Venoms
programme.desc: An unparalleled kung-fu masterpiece from the one and only Chang Cheh. The dying Poison Clan master sends his last pupil on a dangerous mission to hunt down the five titular warriors.

programme.title: The Five Venoms
programme.desc: Sebuah film kung fu yang tak tertandingi dari sutradara film kung fu terbaik, Chang Cheh. Guru dari Klan Racun yang tengah sekarat mengirim murid terakhirnya dalam misi berbahaya untuk memburu lima prajurit.

programme.title: Mission Milano
programme.desc: A wealthy entrepreneur goes undercover with an Interpol agent to protect a new invention, the Seed of God, from falling into an international crime conglomerate.

programme.title: Confinement
programme.desc: Si Ling moves into her dream home after winning an award and hires a confinement nanny. After giving birth to her daughter, inexplicable incidents start happening in the house, threatening both her and her baby.

programme.title: Confinement
programme.desc: Si Ling pindah ke rumah impiannya usai memenangkan penghargaan. Kemudian, ia menyewa pengasuh setelah melahirkan putrinya. Namun, sejumlah kejadian tak terduga terjadi, yang membuat nyawanya dan sang bayi terancam.

programme.title: Distinction
programme.desc: A music teacher in a special needs school, an underachiever from an elite school, and a rebellious teenager with a handicapped brother take part in a campus musical for various reasons. Little did they know that this turns out to be a journey of self-discovery.

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon
programme.desc: Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly carved an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police that ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon
programme.desc: Ho datang ke Hong Kong sebagai imigran gelap pada tahun 1963 dan membangun kerajaan di dunia rahasia para pengedar narkoba dan polisi korup yang memerintah kota di bawah kekuasaan detektif terkenal bernama Lee Rock.

programme.title: Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Lee is the Production head of an advertising firm who tries to improve her team's performance by competing with Creative head Chan in the day and clubbing at Lan Kwai Fong for ideas at night.

programme.title: Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang Lee, Kepala Produksi sebuah agen periklanan yang berusaha meningkatkan kinerja timnya agar dapat mengalahkan Ketua Tim Kreatif Chan dengan dugem di Lan Kwai Fong untuk mendapatkan ide.

programme.title: One And Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the club’s top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: Europe Raiders
programme.desc: Mr Lin and Miss Wang are the two top bounty hunters in the business, and are searching for the destructive missile “Hand of God” to prove who is the better bounty hunter. They soon realize they are not the only ones after the missile. Will Lin and Wang put their differences aside and work together in search for the ‘Hand of God’?

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: An urban sketcher suffering from ALS wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. Then, he asks his old classmate to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Seorang seniman yang menderita ALS ingin memilki kenangan indah karena kondisinya kian memburuk. Ia pun meminta sang mantan teman sekelas untuk memenuhi keinginan terakhirnya dengan menjadi kekasihnya selama satu hari.

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident…

programme.title: Initial D
programme.desc: For five years, 18-year-old Takumi delivers tofu in his fathers near-obsolete Toyota AE86 every morning and because of that, he has become a good racer and also unwillingly perfected the art of drifting.

programme.title: Initial D
programme.desc: Selama lima tahun, Takumi yang berusia 18 tahun mengirimkan tahu setiap pagi dengan mengendarai Toyota AE86 kuno milik ayahnya. Ia pun mengembangkan teknik balap yang sempurna dan menjadi pembalap hebat.

programme.title: Coffin Homes
programme.desc: Set against the housing crisis of Hong Kong, where soaring property prices have driven dwellers to take every insane effort necessary to secure a cramped space, even if it means sharing the same roof with the dead!

programme.title: Coffin Homes
programme.desc: Berlatarkan krisis perumahan di Hong Kong saat melonjaknya harga properti yang memaksa penduduk melakukan segala cara demi mendapatkan sebuah rumah nan sempit, bahkan mereka rela tinggal bersama orang yang sudah mati!

programme.title: Knight Of Shadows: Yin & Yang
programme.desc: Pu Song Ling, a legendary demon hunter, is asked to investigate a case involving missing teenage village girls with Constable Yan Fei and accidentally discover a mysterious love between a knight and a female ghost.

programme.title: Knight Of Shadows: Yin & Yang
programme.desc: Saat menyelidiki kasus sejumlah gadis remaja yang menghilang, Pu Song Ling si pemburu hantu legendaris dan Polisi Yan Fei secara tak sengaja menemukan hubungan asmara antara seorang ksatria dan sesosok hantu wanita.

programme.title: The Lady Iron Chef
programme.desc: Beer girl and part-time model Ceci has terrible cooking skills. Coming from a well-off family that owns a big culinary business, wealthy SK meets Ceci in a gourmet competition held by his family's company. Despite their different backgrounds, Ceci and SK fall for each other. However, SK's dominating mother disapproves of their relationship. To win over her future mother-in-law, Ceci must beat her rival Jade in a gourmet showdown…

programme.title: Miao Miao
programme.desc: Miao Miao is an awkward young beauty who nevertheless enchants her outgoing classmate Xiao Ai. However, Miao Miao discovers her own burgeoning attraction to a sullen CD store owner, and quietly pursues him.

programme.title: Miao Miao
programme.desc: Miao Miao adalah seorang gadis cantik nan canggung yang memikat teman sekelasnya, Xiao Ai. Namun, Miao Miao ternyata jatuh hati kepada seorang pemilik toko CD nan pemarah, dan diam-diam mengejarnya.

programme.title: Chinese Odyssey 2002
programme.desc: Set in Ming Dynasty, young Emperor Zheng De escapes from the palace with his sister who disguised as a man. They run into a notorious wanderer who runs a restaurant with his boyish sister in Jiang Nan. The two pairs of siblings from vastly different social classes descend into an inescapable swirl of gender confusion, slapstick antics and love.

programme.title: Chinese Odyssey 2002
programme.desc: Set in Ming Dynasty, young Emperor Zheng De escapes from the palace with his sister who disguised as a man. They run into a notorious wanderer who runs a restaurant with his boyish sister in Jiang Nan. The two pairs of siblings from vastly different social classes descend into an inescapable swirl of gender confusion, slapstick antics and love.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master
programme.desc: Zhang Wuji yang harus menghadapi serangkaian peristiwa tragis, termasuk kematian orang tuanya dan penindasan oleh aliran-aliran kuat yang mencari rahasia pedang surgawi dan golok naga, dua senjata legendaris yang konon bisa memberikan kekuasaan tak terbatas kepada pemiliknya. Wuji tumbuh dalam pelarian dan dibesarkan oleh berbagai guru bela diri yang membentuknya menjadi seorang pendekar luar biasa.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protégé Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: Sebelum benar-benar menikah, seorang wanita Hong Kong yang baru bertunangan mencoba melepaskan diri dari sebuah pernikahan palsu rahasia dengan seorang pria yang membayarnya bertahun-tahun lalu.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real.

programme.title: Twilight Of Warriors: Walled In
programme.desc: Mengikuti pemuda bermasalah Chan Lok-kwun saat dia secara tidak sengaja memasuki Kota Bertembok, menemukan keteraturan di tengah kekacauan, dan mempelajari pelajaran hidup yang penting di sepanjang jalan.

programme.title: Twilight Of Warriors: Walled In
programme.desc: Follows troubled youth Chan Lok-kwun as he accidentally enters the Walled City, discovers the order amidst its chaos, and learns important life lessons along the way.

programme.title: Those Were The Days
programme.desc: Director Wong despises Cantonese movies of the 60s, but accidentally travels back in time to that movie set. He meets Director Chu, who tells him he can return to modern time if someone likes the film he makes. Wong meets four classic movie stars and invites them to star in his new film, but it flops unexpectedly. Can Wong return to the present?

programme.title: Tales From The Occult
programme.desc: Tales From The Occult merupakan sebuah antologi kuno yang terdiri dari tiga film pendek dan berisi serangkaian kisah baru nan menyeramkan yang tersembunyi di balik suasana perkotaan di Hong Kong.

programme.title: Tales From The Occult
programme.desc: An old school anthology consisting of three short films, Tales from the Occult is the first in a new omnibus series about the hidden horrors that lurk behind the urban landscape of Hong Kong.

programme.title: The Battle At Lake Changjin 2
programme.desc: In this second battle of the war against US aggression and to aid Korea, the 7th Infantry Company is tasked to attack the Water Gate Bridge. Facing extreme weather conditions, the 7th Company risk their lives to successfully destroy the Water Gate Bridge, thereby blocking the US army’s retreat to Xingnan Port.

programme.title: Out Of The Dark
programme.desc: Seorang wanita tua tewas setelah terjatuh dari sebuah gedung dan arwahnya menghantui tempat tersebut. Merasa ketakutan, para penjaga keamanan setempat pun meminta bantuan Leo si pemburu hantu beserta asistennya.

programme.title: Out Of The Dark
programme.desc: An old lady died after falling off a building and her ghost appears to haunt the place. Freaked out by the haunting, the security guards invite ghostbuster Leo and his assistant to help.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs
programme.desc: Ming menyusupi kepolisian atas suruhan triad, sementara Yan adalah polisi yang menyamar sebagai anggota triad. Menjalani kehidupan ganda membuat keduanya merasa terjebak dalam kebohongan dan ingin mencari jalan keluar.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs
programme.desc: Ming is a mole in the police department and Yan is a police mole in the Triads. Leading parallel lives, Ming and Yan are feeling increasingly trapped in their false surroundings and they're desperate to find a way out.

The channel broadcasts over 1,000 episodes of new programs each year, including top quality documentaries such as “A Bite of China”, “Wild Wonders”, and the 100-episode “A History of China”. programme.title: Blood Money
programme.desc: Seorang kartel narkoba Kolombia terpaksa bergabung dengan sebuah kelompok Triad Hong Kong dan seorang pembunuh bayaran nan tampan untuk menyelundupkan kokain ke Australia dan Tiongkok.

programme.title: Blood Money
programme.desc: A Colombian drugs cartel joins forces with a group of Hong Kong Triads and the hottest Hitman on the planet, to ship two tonnes of cocaine into Australia and China.

programme.title: 24 Hours With Katy Perry
programme.desc: How did Katy Perry, the ultimate California girl, transform into an avant-garde fashion siren for the Met Gala? This behind-the-scenes video gives a glimpse at everything it took to go from private jet to after-party, including her gala performance of “Bon Appétit” with Migos.

programme.title: 4 Celebrities: Serial Cheaters
programme.desc: Showbiz is filled with serial cheaters and stories often involve shocking and outlandish behaviors. Watch this video to find out about these 4 celebrities who are serial cheaters.

programme.title: Gold
programme.desc: In the not too distant future, a drifter travelling through the desert discovers the largest gold nugget ever found. He must guard it from thieves amid harsh conditions and wild dogs while waiting for his partner to return.

programme.title: 24 Hours With Ellie Goulding
programme.desc: What does a day in the life of Ellie Goulding look like during quarantine? It starts with bulletproof coffee (heavy on the turmeric) and includes a workout, an elaborate lunch made by her chef brother, and a quick—and safe—stroll outside.

programme.title: 24 Hours With Cole Sprouse
programme.desc: Riverdale's Cole Sprouse gets free coffee, visits some gravestones, and never forgets his camera.

programme.title: 10 Years
programme.desc: The night of their high school reunion, a group of friends realize they still haven't quite grown up in some ways.

programme.title: 7 Riverdale Fans Explain Why...
programme.desc: Seven superfans break down why ‘Riverdale’ is the best show on TV and why you should be watching it. From the show’s murders and conspiracies to the resilience of their favorite characters, these stans make a pretty convincing argument.

programme.title: 73 Questions With D. Zoolander
programme.desc: The international male supermodel gives us a tour of his luxe pad, all while revealing his favorite fashion trend of all time, the truth about his relationship with Hansel, the superpower he wishes he had, and the secret to becoming a model.

programme.title: Platinum
programme.desc: A mysterious man arrives in Houston and gets the opportunity of a lifetime when a pretty hooker with considerable business acumen teaches him the pimp game.

programme.title: 73 Questions With Emma Stone
programme.desc: Emma Stone shows off her fabulous dance moves, belts out a killer Britney Spears impression, and admits to crying in front of Tom Hanks.

programme.title: 24 Hours With Megan Thee
programme.desc: The head hot girl herself as she curls Jordyn Woods’s hair, discusses her favorite horror film (it’s The Evil Dead), and rides horses with the Compton Cowboys.

programme.title: A Vigilante

programme.title: Asia Squawk Box

programme.title: Asia Street Signs
programme.desc: Anchored by Tanvir Gill at the Singapore Exchange (SGX), “Street Signs” follows the day's biggest moves to provide CNBC's audience with actionable, real-time insights. From the anchor desk to trading desks around the region, “Street Signs” helps viewers capitalize on the plays of the day.

programme.title: Fast Money
programme.desc: “Fast Money” is America’s post-market show. Hosted by Melissa Lee and a roundtable of top traders, “Fast Money” breaks through the noise of the day, to bring you the actionable news that matters most to investors.

programme.title: Capital Connection
programme.desc: Hosted by Dan Murphy at NASDAQ Dubai, “Capital Connection” gives you a reading on Asia's markets mid-day and sets you up for the Middle East and European trading day.

programme.title: Europe Squawk Box
programme.desc: Anchored by Steve Sedgwick, Karen Tso and Arabile Gumede, CNBC’s flagship show leads you into and delivers the open of the European markets. Featuring leading business executives, financial strategists and fund managers, “Squawk Box” provides original points of view and instant analysis of the latest business and market news.

programme.title: Europe Street Signs
programme.desc: One hour into Europe’s equity session, Street Signs provides price discovery, the street’s view and a link to the business stories trending online and on social. The show breaks key economic data in Europe and provides live price action in the biggest moving stocks, bonds, currencies and commodities.

programme.title: Worldwide Exchange
programme.desc: Broadcast from CNBC Global Headquarters in Englewood Cliffs, N.J., CNBC’s “Worldwide Exchange” delivers essential, actionable information and analysis for anyone who wants to be part of the global business conversation. Anchored by Frank Holland, the program prepares CNBC’s worldwide audience with a smart take on overnight U.S. news and live international market action.

programme.title: US Squawk Box
programme.desc: “Squawk Box” is the ultimate pre-market morning news and talk program, where the biggest names in business and politics tell their most important stories. Anchored by Joe Kernen, Becky Quick and Andrew Ross Sorkin, the show brings Wall Street to Main Street. It's a must-see for everyone from the professional trader to the casual investor.

programme.title: Squawk On The Street
programme.desc: Headquartered live on the floor of the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE) where the biggest companies in the world trade, “Squawk On The Street” tracks the action of every stock and gives you access to the treasury, currency and commodity action in real time. The show also covers the final hour of European trading, providing investors with actionable insight on the best course of action to take in U.S. based markets.

programme.title: Money Movers
programme.desc: “Money Movers” provides investors with real-time analysis of the stories and the people attracting the attention of the markets each day. Capturing the energy of day’s early trading, the program includes the breaking news and numbers driving stocks and sectors, helping investors make critical decisions. “Money Movers” anchors speak with the CEOs, government decision-makers and newsmakers who play a relevant role in how money is moving.

programme.title: Halftime Report
programme.desc: "Halftime Report" is on the front lines of CNBC's market coverage. Host CNBC’s Scott Wapner and the Street's top investors get to the heart of the action as it's happening and help set the agenda for the rest of the day.

programme.title: The Exchange
programme.desc: When the bell rings, the action does not end. “Closing Bell: Overtime” takes you through all of the after-hours moves including breaking news, corporate earnings and post-market trading. Big investors, smart strategists and top money managers debate actionable ideas and the big market themes of the day, and get viewers ready for tomorrow’s trading day.

programme.title: Power Lunch

Airing CNBC’s award-winning business news coverage, “Power Lunch” delves into the economy, markets, politics, technology and more.

programme.title: Kiko
programme.desc: Kiko tells of a child of a goldfish who is very independent, even though he is an only child. Kiko who is always cheerful has four good friends, namely Lola the discus fish, Ting Ting the crab, Patino the catfish and Poli the betta fish. On the other hand, the antagonists, Karkus the catfish and Pupus the eel, always make Kiko's life chaotic. One day, the lake where Kiko lives is polluted due to the reckless acts of humans, causing Kiko and friends to turn into mutants.

programme.title: Kiko
programme.desc: Kiko, seekor anak ikan mas koki yang sangat mandiri, walaupun ia anak tunggal. Kiko selalu riang dan memiliki empat sahabat baik yaitu Lola si ikan diskus, Ting Ting si kepiting, Patino si ikan patin dan Poli si ikan cupang. Di sisi lain, sosok antagonis, Karkus si ikan lele dan Pupus si belut, selalu membuat ricuh kehidupan Kiko.
